=== EXAMPLE: scdoc_Guides_Tour_of_UGens_ex12 ===

DESCRIPTION: A dark gritty sound, with noise oscillator character around 779 Hz, featuring punchy attack and sustained envelope, with chaotic spectral movement, filtered with resonant_steep_rolloff character, and spectrally sparse.

CATEGORIES:
  attack_time: punchy
  brightness: dark
  crest_factor_db: sustained
  envelope_flatness: flat
  harmonic_to_noise_ratio: gritty
  spectral_complexity_mean: sparse
  spectral_flux_normalized: chaotic
  spectral_slope: steep_rolloff
  temporal_centroid: balanced

SYNTHESIS CONCEPTS (key values):
[oscillator]
  fundamental_freq: 779.4768
  harmonic_decay_rate: -10.8698
  harmonic_regularity: 0.7652
  pitch_clarity: 26.0206
  inharmonicity: 0.3378
  type: noise
[filter]
  spectral_slope: -18.0624
  resonance_freq: 818.2617

SUPERCOLLIDER CODE:
